high_descs: walk to the right to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look up to face the tomato on the back of the table.
Cut the tomato on the back of the sink into slices.
Turn left and walk forward and turn right to face the microwave stand.
Place the knife on the microwave stand.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the tomato on the back of the counter.
Pick up the tomato slice on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave stand.
Place the tomato slice on the left side of the microwave stand.
anns.task_desc: Clean a tomato slice and place it on the left side of the microwave stand.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the coffee maker.
Pick up a knife by the coffee maker.
Turn and go to the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the knife on the counter by the microwave.
Turn and go to the counter by the coffee maker.
Pick up a slice of tomato by the coffee maker.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the slice of tomato in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato on the counter by the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato on the counter by the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the front of the counter with the coffee machine on top.
Pick up the yellow knife between the coffee machine and the gray pot.
Move forward slightly towards the red tomato on the back of the counter.
Slice the red tomato on the counter.
Turn left and go to the small black table with the microwave on top on the right.
Place the knife on the top of the table on the right side of the salt shaker.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the sliced red tomato.
Pick up one slice from the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink across the kitchen on the right.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink under running water.
Turn around and go to the small black table with the microwave on top.
Place the tomato slice on the left front edge in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed tomato slice on the table.
